sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Colum1, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, Colum2, ImgWrap, Img } from './InfoSectionElements' import {Button} from '../ButtonElement' const img = require('../..images/svg-01.svg'); const InfoSection = ({ lightbg, id, imgStart, topLine, heading, lightText, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {heading} {description} ) } export default InfoSection;
